metadata.description:
𝕄𝕚𝕕𝕟𝕚𝕘𝕙𝕥夏季𝔹𝕣𝕖𝕖𝕫𝕖
Is a project about a lonely road. A road where you
the viewer are the last one awake, the last one to see the night.
A moment of stillness, all around you fades to a haze
and you are lost to the midnight summer breeze

Each element in Midnight Breeze has been hand-painted in a 90's anime aesthetic coupled with the Dutchtide tone and flair. 130 different assets with each their own story to tell.
Each Midnight Breeze that is generated is comes banner / wallpaper compatible , think of Discord, Twitter or any other NFT platform.
